  <p>ArenaPlus, the PAGCOR-licensed online sportsbook operated by DigiPlus Interactive, and the National Basketball Association announced a multiyear collaboration on April 27, 2026 that makes ArenaPlus the NBA's first Official Betting Partner in the Philippines. The announcement, made at a star-studded launch event in Manila that drew Philippine sports, entertainment, and gaming-industry figures, marks the highest-profile international-league deal yet secured by a Philippine licensed online sportsbook.</p>

  <p>The deal is structurally significant for three reasons. It is the NBA's first-ever official Philippine betting partner designation. It is the first time a Philippine PAGCOR-licensed sportsbook has secured rights of this scale with a major U.S. professional league. And it lands at the precise moment that the post-delinking Philippine online gaming sector is rebuilding its consumer-engagement architecture and looking for the kind of marketing tentpole that an NBA association uniquely provides.</p>

